OL,3,CTwo people arrested after car crashes
OL,4,Cinto Belfast house
OL,6,FTwo people who were arrested after a
OL,7,Fcar crashed into a house in Belfast
OL,8,Fearly on Monday, have been released on
OL,9,Fbail.
OL,11,FThe PSNI said it received a call at
OL,12,Faround 3.45am that a blue Volkswagen
OL,13,FGolf had driven into a wall and a
OL,14,Fconservatory of a home in Dorchester
OL,15,FPark in the south of the city.
OL,17,FThe crash caused "extensive damage" to
OL,18,Fthe car, the property and three other
OL,19,Fvehicles in the area.
OL,26,@yD@ROUyD@cO]
