OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779894668
OL,3,CTwo people arrested after car crashes
OL,4,Cinto Belfast house
OL,6,FInspector Colhoun said: "A short time
OL,7,Flater, officers located two people
OL,8,Fsuspected of being in the offending
OL,9,Fvehicle."
OL,11,FThe man, 21, and woman, 33, were
OL,12,Farrested on suspicion of a number of
OL,13,Foffences including dangerous driving
OL,14,Fand driving while unfit.
OL,16,F"This is a shocking incident, and it's
OL,17,Fonly by sheer luck that we aren't
OL,18,Fdealing with much more serious
OL,19,Fconsequences this morning," Inspector
OL,20,FColhoun said.
