OL,3,CTwo people arrested after car crashes
OL,4,Cinto Belfast house
OL,6,F"The residents of the property had to
OL,7,Fbe moved in the middle of the night,
OL,8,Fwhich was an extremely distressing
OL,9,Fexperience for them."
OL,11,FPolice are appealing for any witnesses
OL,12,For anyone who saw the car in the
OL,13,FMilltown Road or Malone Road areas to
OL,14,Fcontact them.JCatch up with the latest
OL,15,FUTV Live on ITVX
